reviewText: My grandson loves this video. He is into dinasours right now.
My son loves Chuggington, and this is an easy way to keep him occupied for a little while.
Purchased for my grandson and he loves it!
My son LOVES Chuggington. We bought this to add to his collection.

There are two topics my 2 year old grandson enjoys - trains and dinosaurs. This DVD's theme is exactly what will please him. The other animated train series also had dinosaurs DVD's but for some reason he looses interest watching "Thomas the Train" DVD's. I suspect they are geared towards older children.
Daughter loves videos, so that says it all.
